01:22.661 --> 01:26.445
Since when?

01:26.445 --> 01:28.569
Ha, ha.  Funny man.

01:28.569 --> 01:30.176
Excuse me, I'll take care of this.

01:30.176 --> 01:31.759
Oh, thank you Niles.

01:31.759 --> 01:34.994
What's new, Niles?

