01:39.983 --> 01:44.731
Oh, my God!  I had no idea.  I can't believe no-one told me.

01:44.731 --> 01:49.430
This is such a surprise!
That's enough, Talulah.

01:49.430 --> 01:52.062
You're not fooling anyone.

01:52.062 --> 01:54.777
I'm sorry sir, your card didn't clear.

01:54.777 --> 01:56.360
I have to do this.

01:56.360 --> 01:59.237
Wait, wait!  What are you doing?

01:59.237 --> 02:04.272
The computer said "credit cancelled by order of co-signatory."

02:04.272 --> 02:06.414
