02:17.151 --> 02:19.088
And my bank accounts.

02:19.088 --> 02:23.237
And my phone service!

02:25.759 --> 02:29.660
Doc, I'm at the airport, and I'm having a lot of trouble getting on the plane.

02:29.660 --> 02:33.471
Now Bob, statistics prove that we're safer in the air than on the ground.

02:33.471 --> 02:40.612
That-that's not it.  I'm supposed to be flying home to Newark for Christmas,
but the flight the next gate over has a flight to Maui.

02:40.612 --> 02:44.538
I'm telling you, it's calling me, Doc.

02:44.538 --> 02:47.262
Why are you hesitant to go home?

02:47.262 --> 02:49.429
