18:02.074 --> 18:04.991
Oh, yeah. This one still has the tags on it.

18:04.991 --> 18:08.142
Look, this isn't the kind of conversation we should be having on Christmas eve.

18:08.142 --> 18:12.624
No, Dad?  Well, what was it you wanted to say?

18:12.624 --> 18:19.493
Well, you know Frasier, you're always giving people things you think they should like,
instead of things that they really like.

18:19.493 --> 18:21.345
I mean, come on -

18:21.345 --> 18:25.438
In your entire life, have you ever seen me wear anything like that?

18:25.438 --> 18:28.515
Well, no.  I thought you might like a change.

18:28.515 --> 18:31.626
Well, it's like when you were a kid, remember?

18:31.626 --> 18:36.797
I wanted you to love baseball.  I wanted to get you a bat, glove, everything, for Christmas.

18:36.797 --> 18:40.700
But you had your mind set on a microscope, so that's what I got you.

18:40.700 --> 18:52.525
And then when Dad took us to a game, you spent the whole time looking for rodent hairs in your hot-dog.

18:52.525 --> 18:57.837
I'm just saying Christmas isn't the time you try to mold somebody,
which is what you're trying to do with Frederick.

18:57.837 --> 18:59.934
I think I know what's good for my own son.

18:59.934 --> 19:01.362
I brushed my teeth, Daddy.

19:01.362 --> 19:04.600
Oh, that's my boy.  Come on.

19:04.600 --> 19:08.086
Bonsoir, Uncle Niles.
Et toi aussi.

19:08.086 --> 19:09.713
Hey, you'd better get to sleep, or Santa won't come.

19:09.713 --> 19:13.242
OK.  I know just what Santa's bringing me this year, Dad.

19:13.242 --> 19:16.032
I bet you don't.

19:16.032 --> 19:22.625
Yes I do too.  It's an Outlaw Laser Robo Geek.

19:24.767 --> 19:26.485
What makes you think that?

19:26.485 --> 19:28.927
Because I asked Santa for it in my letter.

19:28.927 --> 19:32.255
They are sooo cool.

19:32.255 --> 19:35.407
Ahh, listen ahh, Frederick,

19:35.407 --> 19:38.130
there's erm... Frederick, where are you going?

19:38.130 --> 19:43.175
I'm going to make myself fall asleep right away, so the next thing I know, it'll be morning.

19:43.175 --> 19:44.220
Goodnight, Daddy.

19:44.220 --> 19:45.718
I'll come in and tuck you in, in a minute.

19:45.718 --> 19:47.510
Goodnight, Grandpa.  Goodnight, Uncle Niles.

19:47.510 --> 19:48.196
Goodnight.

19:48.196 --> 19:52.886
Goodnight, Frederick.  I'm going to go home and go to bed too.

19:52.886 --> 19:57.351
I hope Aunt Maris comes out of her coma.

20:06.967 --> 20:12.524
He asked where she was, I thought the truth would just upset him.

20:12.524 --> 20:14.391
I'll see you in the morning.  Merry Christmas.

20:14.391 --> 20:16.992
See you tomorrow.

20:17.896 --> 20:20.016
Well, this is turning out to be quite a Christmas.

20:20.016 --> 20:23.691
Oh, it's going to be fine.

20:23.691 --> 20:25.640
Done it again.

20:25.640 --> 20:28.695
Gotten everyone the wrong gifts.

20:28.695 --> 20:31.899
What is it about me?

20:31.899 --> 20:34.357
Well, here, you might as well open your gift now.

20:34.357 --> 20:36.147
No reason for everyone to be disappointed tomorrow.

20:36.147 --> 20:38.972
Hey, I'm sure I'm gonna love it.

20:38.972 --> 20:43.957
I doubt it.  Not exactly my night.

20:45.114 --> 20:49.288
Hey!  A robe!  Great, I love it!

20:49.288 --> 20:55.140
No, you don't.  It's not a robe, it's a dressing gown.

20:55.140 --> 20:57.415
Noel Coward would love it, but it's not you.

20:57.415 --> 21:00.070
Hey, I love Noel Coward!

21:00.070 --> 21:01.720
Dad, you're overcompensating.

21:01.720 --> 21:05.755
Some people are hard to buy for, I'm sorry.

21:05.755 --> 21:09.331
But, you know, you are too, I never know what to get you.

21:09.331 --> 21:11.540
Here.

21:11.540 --> 21:14.605
You might as well open this now.

21:16.224 --> 21:20.617
Yeah.  Guess it was easier when I was small.

21:20.617 --> 21:23.055
'Cause kids always know what they want, don't they?

21:23.055 --> 21:26.579
Yeah, yeah.  It's rough for adults.

21:31.277 --> 21:32.843
Oh, Dad...

21:32.843 --> 21:36.937
Merry Christmas, son.

21:36.937 --> 21:39.038
How did you know?  It's jut what I always wanted:

21:39.038 --> 21:45.779
My very own Outlaw Laser Robo Geek.

21:46.357 --> 21:50.774
Oh, Dad - oh, oh, listen, are the batteries included?

21:50.774 --> 21:54.465
In the box.
Oh, Dad!

